product_meta.title: Wall Mounted Key Lock Box with 10-Digit Push Button Combination — Perfect for Guests, Tenants, Realtors, Contractors, Spare Key Storage at Home or Office — Exterior Waterproof Cover and Mounting Kit
feature_bullets: DURABLE METAL CONSTRUCTION. Permanent wall mounted lock box keeps up to four house keys safe. Both the base and door of the box are made from heavy gauge all-weather zinc alloy. Front door of box is a separate piece that is removable when opened. (Interior key storage space is 2.8"x1.6"1.0" in size, and will fit most standard sized keys. However, some car keys and fobs may be a bit too large.)
QUICK, EASY, SECURE INSTALLATION. Includes four plastic screws and screw anchors for mounting. Install on any solid surface indoor or outdoors.

PUSH BUTTON KEY PAD. Hundreds of possible combinations for passcodes three to ten digits long. Easier than a dial, even in low light conditions. The lock box kit includes instructions and a small tool to help in setting the passcode. Easy access for children, the elderly, or in low-light conditions. (Note: passcodes do not need to be entered in the correct sequence. For example, a passcode of 67890 can also be entered as 09876.)

INDOOR / OUTDOOR USE. Thick, zinc alloy, impact-resistant frame protects your box in any weather. The lock box also includes a detachable weather-resistant rubber cover for even more protection from snow, ice, and rain.

SECURE HOME ACCESS. Avoid lock-outs and share keys with realtors, contractors, family members and renters. Ideal for residential or commercial use. Secure private homes, apartments, vacation rentals, utility buildings, and construction sites.
